Story
Once upon a time, in a forest there lived a Monkey who rested on a Banana Tree, which was on the banks of a river. In the same forest there live a Crocodile and his Wife.
Monkey is a very kind person. One day, the Crocodile came to the Banks of the river and rested under that tree. The Kind hearted Monkey offered him some fruits.
The Crocodile came back the next day for more fruits, as he loved them. As days passed by, Monkey and Crocodile became good friends.
